original: Eklund, Uno Ragnar Emanuel, komminister, Göteborg, f. 4/12/06 i Eksjö av metodistpastor C. J. E. o. Emilia Persson. G. 37 m. Inger Sofia Kristina Svenæus. Barn : Monika Barbro Kristina f. 38. — Stud:ex. i Kalmar 26, teol. fii. ex. 29, teol. kand., prakt, teol. prov o. prästv. f. Linköp. stift 3’2. Past :adj. i Linköp. 33’, bitr. stifts-adj. där s. å., stiftsadj. 34, kommin. i Rumskulla 37, pred. v. Johanneskyr-kan i Gbg 38, kommin. i Johannebergs förs. i Gbg sed. 44, mil:pastor v. Västkustens marindistr. sed. 42, pred. v. Carlanderska sjukhemm. sed. 43. Ordf. i Gbgs kristl. ungd:råd o. i Johannebergs scoutkårråd, led. av S:t Johan-neskyrkans kyrkoråd, av styr. f. Gbgs kyrkl. sjöm:vård o. av styr. f. sällsk. Jultomtarna i Gbg, led. av kyrkofullm. sed. 47. Skr.: Soli Deo Gloria (41), På heligt rum (43), medv. i Epistel postilla (42), Aftonsångspostilla (46), medarb. i Stiftskrönikan m. fl. tidskr.
translated: Eklund, Uno Ragnar Emanuel, parish minister, Gothenburg, b. December 4, 1906 in Eksjö to Methodist pastor C. J. E. and Emilia Persson. Married in 1937 to Inger Sofia Kristina Svenæus. Children: Monika Barbro Kristina b. 1938. Education: Graduated from high school in Kalmar in 1926, theological studies in 1929, practical theological studies, ordination and priestly service in the Linköping diocese in 1932. Positions held: Assistant pastor in Linköping in 1933, assistant diocesan pastor in the same year, diocesan pastor in 1934, parish minister in Rumskulla in 1937, preacher at the Johannes Church in Gothenburg in 1938, parish minister in Johanneberg parish in Gothenburg since 1944, military pastor for the West Coast naval district since 1942, preacher at the Carlanderska Hospital since 1943. Held positions as chairman of Gothenburg's Christian youth council and the Johanneberg scout troop council, member of the St. Johannes Church council, the board of Gothenburg's church maritime care, the board of the society Jultomtarna in Gothenburg, and member of the church council since 1947. Written works include "Soli Deo Gloria" (1941), "På heligt rum" (1943), co-author of "Epistel postilla" (1942), "Aftonsångspostilla" (1946), and contributor to "Stiftskrönikan" and other journals.
